social_posts.post_text: I might need my own animated series now 😂
“I’m not a 🐐 but I fit the description”
Giannis…absolutely worth the price of admission…🫢🏀
I’m gonna have to apply for citizenship ASAP
Home is where the turf is 🇺🇸

What a honor it was to get field level access at the legendary Maracanã stadium, the same place the 1950 and 2014 World Cups were played 🙏🏿. 

I still have the chills from walking into the stadium from the tunnel… 

Thank you also to the staff there for letting me take penalty kicks on the pitch ⚽️. 

Let me know if you need me for Copa América 🤪.
Great to see family this weekend…happy Friday y’all 🎉
First soccer match ever and I got to see Messi play AND score a goal…insane…
Excited to get back on the tennis courts real soon… 🤗🎾 #loading⏳
All I want for Christmas is an i8 😩😍
Wishing all my friends and family a happy and healthy new year 🎊

RCS | Choate | Tufts | Johns Hopkins MBA | World Traveler
“If you want what they have, do what they do.”
